      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at some old photos today and i didnt even recognize the person looking back at me. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago. now im just... i dont know. just going through the motions. like a ghost inhabiting a body that doesnt belong to me anymore. i feel like a walking corpse.",
